dc_description_s: This data layer represents recreation (boat launch locations) for Bayfield County in 2020. [This layer contains boat landing access points for lakes in Bayfield County. Link to metadata information: https://www.bayfieldcounty.org/437/GIS-Metadata]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: [https://www.bayfieldcounty.org/892/GIS-Data-Download]
